    formationText: "The soul is the spiritual part of us that makes each person alive, unique, and open to God. The Church teaches that God creates each human soul directly and that it is immortal. We are not souls trapped in bodies, nor bodies that happen to think. We are a single person, body and soul together.\n\nThis gives every human life immense dignity. Your worth does not come from what you produce or how you look. It comes from being a person made in God\u2019s image, body and soul, loved into existence and destined for eternal life with him.",
